Main doc:

    This module makes using of (layers') clipping windows much easier.

    Usage:
      clip(window:PTR TO window,x1,y1,x2,y2)

      unclip(window:PTR TO window)

      window - pointer to clipped window
      x1,y1  - start coordinates
      x2,y2  - finish coordinates

      e.g.: ...code...
            layersbase:=OpenLibrary('layers.library',0)
            ...code...
            clip(window,window.borderleft,window.bordertop,window.width-window.borderright-1,window.height-window.borderbottom-1)
            ...code...
            unclip(window)
            ...code...
            CloseLibrary(layersbase)
            ...code...

Requirements:
  For module: AmigaE3.0a
  For Cliptest.e: AmigaE3.2a

